[i][b]An aspiring actress finds her hopes of big-screen stardom unexpectedly complicated when she is forced to contend with an unplanned pregnancy. All Anna ever wanted was to become an actress. A pretty girl from a wealthy family, Anna one day decides to pack her bags and head to Copenhagen without telling her mother and father. Once in the city, however, Anna discovers just what a cruel mistress fate can be upon discovering that she will soon become a mother. Later, after giving birth to a baby girl, Anna does her best to provide for her daughter while still pursuing her dreams of becoming a famous actress. Unfortunately for mother and daughter alike, this path ultimately proves to have tragic consequences.
